<h5 class="text-center mb-3"><strong>Thanks for trusting us with your essay! &#128522;</strong></h5>
<p class="text-center mb-5">Please see your submission details below. Your essay is currently being processed, and we'll get back to you within 24 hours with an email sharing payment details and instructions.</p>


<h5 class="mb-3 text-center"><strong>Submission Details</strong></h5>
<p class="mb-0"><strong>Student name</strong>: <%= @essay.student_name %></p>
<p class="mb-0"><strong>Email</strong>: <%= @essay.email %></p>
<p class="mb-0"><strong>Applicant type</strong>: <%= @essay.applicant_type %></p>
<p class="mb-0"><strong>Country Applying To</strong>: <%= @essay.country_applying %></p>
<% if @essay.university_applying.present? %>
  <p class="mb-0"><strong>University Applying To</strong>: <%= @essay.university_applying %></p>
<% end %>
<% if @essay.program_applying.present? %>
  <p class="mb-0"><strong>Program Applying To</strong>: <%= @essay.program_applying %></p>
<% end %>

<p class="mb-0 mt-3"><strong>Essay prompt</strong>: <%= @essay.prompt %></p>
<p class="mb-0"><strong>Essay word count</strong>: <%= @essay.word_count %> words</p>
<p><strong>Price</strong>: $<%= @essay.essay_price %> (USD)</p>

<p class="text-center"><strong>Essay:</strong></p>
<p><%= simple_format(strip_tags(@essay.essay)) %></p>

<div class="mt-5">
  <%= link_to "< back to Home", root_path %>
</div>

<div class="center">
  <%#= link_to "Back to Home", root_path, class: "main-btn" %>
</div>
